response.original_title: Secret UFO Files: Strange Stories of Alien Encounters
response.overview: Contemporary historians have posed the suggestion that ancient man was visited by time traveling men or beings from the distant future who were mistaken as Gods, wielding biological and technological technologies that were far beyond early man's comprehension. This cosmic phenomenon could have reset mankind's intended natural evolutionary course in history, that has continued to flourish throughout the centuries.
response.title: Secret UFO Files: Strange Stories of Alien Encounters
